textfsm_template:
Value SERIAL_NUMBER (\S+)
Value MODEL (\S+)
Value VENDOR (.+)
Value HARDWARE_REVISION (\S+)
Value SOFTWARE_VERSION (\S+)
Value PLATFORM (\S+)

Start
  ^Serial Number\s+:\s+${SERIAL_NUMBER} -> Record
  ^Model\s+:\s+${MODEL}
  ^Vendor\s+:\s+${VENDOR}
  ^Hardware Revision\s+:\s+${HARDWARE_REVISION}
  ^Software Version\s+:\s+${SOFTWARE_VERSION}
  ^Platform\s+:\s+${PLATFORM}
